---
title: `$anemon::step()`
description: Create list of _namespace_ steps from a string.
...

~~~ .php.xmp
Anemon::step($input, $NS = '.', $dir = 1);
~~~

**Example:**

~~~ .php
$test_1 = Anemon::step('foo.bar.baz');
~~~

Result:

~~~ .php
$test_1 = [
    'foo.bar.baz',
    'foo.bar',
    'foo'
];
~~~

If `$dir` is set to `-1`, the steps will be ordered from the first part:

~~~
$test_2 = Anemon::step('foo.bar.baz', '.', -1);
~~~

Result:

~~~ .php
$test_2 = [
    'foo.bar.baz',
    'bar.baz',
    'baz'
];
~~~